collective communication library for stdml


features

MPI compatiable interface (*)
elastic support (*)
async interface (*)
unified interface for hetogeneous device (TODO: CUDA, http://github.com/lgarithm/stdcuda)
point to point APIs (TODO)
extentable protocol (*)
dependency free, pure modern c++ (TODO: cleanup go dependency)


TensorFlow binding: https://github.com/stdml/stdml-collective-tensorflow-experimental
PyTorch binding: https://github.com/stdml/stdml-collective-pytorch-experimental
